{"tid":917714,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"我去睇咗一場英超","createTime":"2018-11-26T15:28:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T23:35:25.000Z","uid":99568,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"77141a2b7dceda48f499b30c504cc2db5cc6ad43","tid":917714,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T15:28:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sd13q4i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSd13q4i.jpg&h=5b6879c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為已經唔係第一次睇去睇愛華頓所以我冇影好多相<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我早咗成個鐘入場所以好有幸好近距離睇到 英格蘭首席門將jordan pickford<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/41oJq4S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F41oJq4S.jpg&h=e2f57292&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7TcmXbz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7TcmXbz.jpg&h=73dc804a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tpvr8ig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftpvr8ig.jpg&h=207a67b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t7sBL4Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft7sBL4Z.jpg&h=323a0925&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢一幅相佢係同緊企喺我隔籬嗰位細路仔say hi揮手<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KJxKaw4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKJxKaw4.jpg&h=a0a27a3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住呢幾幅相就係我坐嘅位置<br />\n呢個位個個景觀好麻麻<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6yRyOjb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yRyOjb.jpg&h=5ad69582&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fJ5r8jd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfJ5r8jd.jpg&h=6a7f4a5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZKUwzZf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZKUwzZf.jpg&h=9994963f&s={SIZE}\" 